## 14-HARDENING. Forensic Signal Integrity (txsig)
Eliminated false positives for duplicate transactions using spatial entropy:
- **[transaction.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/types/transaction.ts)**: Added `source_locator` for PDF coordinates.
- **[txsig.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ledger/txsig.ts)**: Updated hash formula to include `p{page}:y{y_coord}` if present.
- **[txsig_collision.test.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/tests/txsig_collision.test.ts)**: Proven that identical content on different lines produces distinct hashes.

