## 15. Production Hardening & Resilience
Guaranteed the system's durability under operational stress:
- **[system_guard.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/core/system_guard.ts)**: Implemented global safety states (READ_ONLY, BRAIN_DISABLED) for emergency degradation.
- **[ingestion.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/core/ingestion.ts)**: Added idempotent skip logic (safe-skip duplicates) to prevent destructive re-processing.
- **[recovery.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/core/recovery.ts)**: Built [LedgerReconstructor](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/core/recovery.ts#10-43) for full state restoration from AuditLog streams.
- **[resilience.test.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/tests/resilience.test.ts)**: Verified safe degradation, recovery, and idempotency guarantees.

